OL,3,C'People were dying all around' -
OL,4,Ccaptain on Mediterranean rescue mission
OL,6,FA Devon captain helped rescue 100
OL,7,Fpeople when he came to the aid of a
OL,8,Fsinking boat in the Mediterranean.
OL,10,FCaptain Richard Gascoyne Kirkby, from
OL,11,FExeter, and three other crewmen of the
OL,12,FMayan Queen - a luxury yacht - changed
OL,13,Fcourse to answer a distress call off
OL,14,Fthe coast of Greece in June last year.
OL,16,FRichard answered the mayday call when
OL,17,Fhe was en route to Crete.
OL,19,FThe sinking ship was nearly 50
OL,20,Fnautical miles from land.
