OL,3,C'People were dying all around' -
OL,4,Ccaptain on Mediterranean rescue mission
OL,6,FHe said: "We got really close and
OL,7,Fcould hear screams from the water.
OL,9,F"We launched our rescue boat and
OL,10,Fpulled out as many people, as quickly,
OL,11,Fas we could.
OL,13,F"People were dying all around us."
OL,15,FSadly many people drowned, including
OL,16,Fwomen and children, but the crew
OL,17,Fmanaged to rescue more than 100 people.
OL,19,FRichard said: "Once they came on board
OL,20,Fto us, they were in a bad way. They'd
OL,21,Fseen family members dying."
