OL,3,C'People were dying all around' -
OL,4,Ccaptain on Mediterranean rescue mission
OL,6,FCaptain Kirkby and his fellow sailors
OL,7,F- Coxswain Ben Owen Bramwell, Trystan
OL,8,FTanner and Bosun Ashley Oliver West -
OL,9,Fhave been recognised for going beyond
OL,10,Ftheir call of duty with the Merchant
OL,11,FNavy Medal.
OL,13,FRichard said: "We did it, and we did
OL,14,Fit well. I'd like to thank all the
OL,15,Fcrew and everyone out there that saved
OL,16,Flives at sea."
OL,18,FMaritime Minister Mike Kane said:
OL,19,F"Their dedication, bravery and
OL,20,Ffortitude is truly inspiring and shows
OL,21,Fthe very best of UK maritime.
