OL,6,F"I take pride in celebrating these
OL,7,Findividuals, as well as the many
OL,8,Fseafarers who make such a significant
OL,9,Fcontribution to our country, both here
OL,10,Fand abroad."
OL,12,FRecipients of the Merchant Navy Medal
OL,13,Ffor Meritorious Service will receive
OL,14,Ftheir medal on 5 November in a
OL,15,Fceremony with HRH Princess Anne.
